Package: DepMod
Title: Decision-Analytic Modelling for Depression Prevention and Treatment
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Stijn", "Peeters", , "s.b.peeters@eshpm.eur.nl", role = c("aut", "cre"),comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0004-3684-3584")),
    person("Frederick", "Thielen", ,"thielen@eshpm.eur.nl", role = c("aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0312-5891")),
    person("Ben", "Wijnen", , "bwijnen@trimbos.nl", role = c("aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7993-1905"))
    )
Description: Provides functions and example datasets to run a decision-analytic model
    for prevention and treatment strategies across depression severity states
    (sub-clinical, mild, moderate, severe, and recurrent). The package supports
    scenario analyses (base and alternative inputs) and summarises outcomes such
    as coverage, adherence, effect sizes, and healthcare costs.
